title: MAGNIFICENT WATER VIEW IN BISCAYNE BEACH!!
posting_body: ['Enjoy this magnificent unit with direct bay views in the newest and most luxurious building in East Edgewater.', '1 bedroom + spacious den,2 bathrooms with 110 SQ.FT terrace.', 'Private elevator, walk-in closets, top of the line appliances, window treatments, incredible Bay views from every room.', "Biscayne Beach's interiors were designed by renowned Bravo star and design expert Thom Filicia.", 'Luxury amenities including 2 pools, cabanas, beach club, state of the art gym, spa, tennis courts.', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
